Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:21:59.83,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Burning Love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:07.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}アマいだけなら
